:Matrix3</code> (element of SO(3)) as well as <code>math::Matrix4</code> (element of SE(3)), but the <code>math::Matrix3</code> class is missing several useful operations like matrix inversion and conversion back into a rotation. </p>\n<p>Are there any plans to clean up the math component?</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "wontfix", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-10-30T23:31:43.507607+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-02-02T17:22:50.138098+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 929}